Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:42.63,Default,Ken,0,0,0,,Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:44.82,Default,Ken,0,0,0,,Cậu hỏi đi.
